Rick & Morty WebApp â€” Full-Stack Assignment

A full-stack Angular + .NET 9 application exploring Rick & Morty characters

Overview

This project is a full-stack web application built as part of a technical assignment.
It fetches characters from the Rick & Morty API, allows search, filtering, and viewing detailed character information, including episodes, origin, and location.

Tech Stack
Frontend (Client)

Angular 17+ (Stand-alone components)

TypeScript

RxJS

HTML + CSS

Backend (Server)

.NET 9 Minimal API

C#

HttpClient

CORS enabled

